---
import { site } from "../content/home";
import { landing } from "../content/landing";
const fc = landing.footer;
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Strategic Personal Branding — Version B</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Position-first personal branding for founders who have outgrown word of mouth. Book a strategy call." />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=Raleway:ital,wght@0,500;0,600;0,700;1,500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg:         #ffffff;
      --bg2:        #f4f5f7;
      --bg3:        #eceef2;
      --text:       #0f172a;
      --muted:      #64748b;
      --accent:     #2563eb;
      --accent-dim: #1d4ed8;
      --accent-soft: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.12);
      --accent-border: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.35);
      --title-dim:  #94a3b8;
      --title-on:   #020617;
      --ft:         "Raleway", system-ui, sans-serif;
      --fb:         "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;
      --pad:        clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
      --sec:        clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
      --max:        680px;
      --max-wide:   920px;
      --nav-h:      4.5rem;
      /* Measured nav height for scroll-padding / anchors only */
      --v2-nav-pad: 5.75rem;
    }

    html { overflow-x: hidden; scroll-padding-top: calc(var(--v2-nav-pad) + env(safe-area-inset-top, 0px)); }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: var(--fb);
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    #v2-nav {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      z-index: 200;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
      min-height: var(--nav-h);
      padding: 0.75rem var(--pad);
      padding-top: max(0.75rem, env(safe-area-inset-top, 0px));
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
    }
    .v2-logo { font-family: var(--ft); font-size: 1.0625rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .v2-nav-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: flex-end; }
    .v2-ver-link {
      font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none;
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12); border-radius: 999px; padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
    }
    .v2-ver-link:hover { color: var(--text); border-color: var(--accent-border); }
    .v2-cta {
      font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent);
      border: 1px solid var(--accent-border); border-radius: 999px; padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem; text-decoration: none;
    }
    .v2-cta:hover { background: var(--accent-soft); }

    .v2-wrap { max-width: var(--max-wide); margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 var(--pad); }

    section {
      padding-block: var(--sec);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
    }
    section:first-of-type { border-top: none; }

    .v2-center { text-align: center; }
    .v2-eyebrow {
      font-family: var(--fb);
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      display: block;
    }
    /* Hero intro: large eyebrow; both lines inherit same size so shrink tween stays smooth */
    .v2-eyebrow.v2-eyebrow--intro {
      font-family: var(--ft);
      font-size: clamp(1.65rem, 4.5vw, 2.85rem);
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      line-height: 1.12;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
      transform-origin: 50% 0%;
      will-change: transform, font-size;
    }
    .v2-hero-section {
      min-height: min(100dvh, calc(100svh - var(--v2-nav-pad, 5.75rem)));
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      padding-top: max(0.5rem, var(--v2-nav-pad, 5.75rem));
      padding-bottom: 2rem;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      overflow-x: visible;
      overflow-y: visible;
    }
    .v2-hero-section.v2-center { text-align: center; }
    [data-v2-hero-inner] {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 0.35rem;
      opacity: 0;
      visibility: hidden;
      pointer-events: none;
      overflow: visible;
    }
    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      [data-v2-hero-inner] {
        opacity: 1 !important;
        visibility: visible !important;
        pointer-events: auto !important;
      }
    }
    [data-v2-hero-rest] {
      margin-top: auto;
      width: 100%;
      opacity: 0;
      visibility: hidden;
    }
    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      [data-v2-hero-rest] {
        opacity: 1 !important;
        visibility: visible !important;
      }
    }
    .v2-hero-eyebrow-wrap {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
      line-height: 1.02;
    }
    .v2-hero-eyebrow-wrap .v2-hero-eyebrow-line {
      display: block;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      line-height: 1.05;
      width: max-content;
      max-width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .v2-eyebrow .v2-tw-word {
      font: inherit;
      letter-spacing: inherit;
      text-transform: inherit;
      color: inherit;
    }
    /* Second line: one line while large and after shrink (scroll if needed on tiny screens). */
    [data-v2-eyebrow-l2] {
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .v2-eyebrow.v2-eyebrow--intro.v2-hero-eyebrow-wrap {
      max-width: 100%;
      overflow: visible;
    }
    .v2-hero-title-shell {
      transform-origin: 50% 0%;
      max-width: min(100%, 44rem);
      margin-inline: auto;
      min-width: 0;
      overflow-x: auto;
      overflow-y: visible;
      scrollbar-width: none;
      -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    }
    .v2-hero-title-shell::-webkit-scrollbar {
      display: none;
    }
    /* One continuous line: prefix … “generate” + morph (scroll horizontally on narrow viewports). */
    .v2-hero-title {
      display: block;
      white-space: nowrap;
      width: max-content;
      max-width: none;
      font-family: var(--ft);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5.5vw, 3.25rem);
      line-height: 1.18;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .v2-hero-title-prefix {
      display: inline;
      text-align: inherit;
    }
    .v2-hero-morph-clip {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-left: 0.14em;
      vertical-align: baseline;
      max-width: none;
      overflow: visible;
    }
    /* Same size as the headline; accent colour. clip-path wipe is applied in JS. */
    [data-v2-hero-morph] {
      display: inline-block;
      font: inherit;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--accent);
      letter-spacing: inherit;
      line-height: inherit;
      vertical-align: baseline;
      will-change: clip-path;
    }
    .v2-tw-char {
      display: inline;
      opacity: 0;
      will-change: opacity;
    }
    .v2-tw-word {
      will-change: opacity;
    }
    .v2-h2 {
      font-family: var(--ft); font-weight: 700; font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.2vw, 2.15rem);
      line-height: 1.28; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 1rem;
      max-width: 42rem; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;
      text-wrap: balance;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .v2-h3 { font-family: var(--ft); font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.125rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--text); }
    .v2-p { color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 1rem; max-width: var(--max); margin-inline: auto; }
    .v2-p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .v2-p--wide { max-width: 52rem; margin-inline: auto; }
    .v2-p--left { margin-inline: 0; text-align: left; max-width: 100%; }
    .v2-strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }
    .v2-accent { color: var(--accent); }

    /* Titles: normal wrapping (do NOT use nbsp between words in JS) */
    [data-v2-reveal-title] {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 100%;
      white-space: normal;
      overflow-wrap: break-word;
      word-wrap: break-word;
    }
    /* Initial colour before GSAP runs; GSAP tweens inline color (no !important) */
    [data-v2-reveal-title] .v2-word {
      font-family: var(--ft);
      color: var(--title-dim);
    }

    .v2-btn {
      display: inline-block; margin-top: 1.25rem; padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
      font-family: var(--fb);
      font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9375rem; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--accent); color: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--accent-dim);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.25);
      transition: filter 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    .v2-btn:hover { filter: brightness(1.05); box-shadow: 0 6px 28px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.32); }
    .v2-btn-lg { padding: 1rem 2.25rem; font-size: 1rem; }

    .v2-pain-grid {
      display: grid; gap: 1rem;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    @media (min-width: 720px) {
      .v2-pain-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    }
    .v2-pain-card {
      background: var(--bg2);
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.35rem 1.5rem;
      text-align: left;
      transition: box-shadow 0.25s ease, border-color 0.25s ease;
    }
    .v2-pain-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.22);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.08);
    }
    .v2-pain-card h3 { font-family: var(--ft); font-size: 1.0625rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.65rem; color: var(--text); }
    .v2-pain-label {
      font-family: var(--fb);
      font-size: 0.625rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .v2-pain-quote { font-style: italic; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 0.65rem; font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.55; }
    .v2-pain-body { font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }

    .v2-pull {
      font-family: var(--ft); font-weight: 700;
      font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 2.8vw, 1.85rem);
      line-height: 1.35;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 2rem auto 0;
      max-width: 42rem;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .v2-obj { margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
    .v2-obj:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .v2-obj-q {
      background: var(--bg2);
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
      border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 0.9375rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .v2-obj-a .v2-p { margin-inline: 0; text-align: left; max-width: none; }

    .v2-split { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2.25rem; text-align: left; margin-top: 1.5rem; }
    @media (max-width: 780px) { .v2-split { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    .v2-split-col h3 {
      font-family: var(--fb);
      font-size: 0.6875rem; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .v2-split-col--for h3 { color: var(--accent); }
    .v2-split-col--not h3 { color: var(--muted); }
    .v2-prose p { font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.65; }
    .v2-prose p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .v2-split-col--not ul { list-style: none; }
    .v2-split-col--not li {
      font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      padding-left: 0.5rem; border-left: 2px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.1);
    }

    .v2-step { margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06); text-align: left; }
    .v2-step:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; margin-bottom: 0; padding-bottom: 0; }
    .v2-step-num { font-family: var(--fb); font-size: 0.625rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.14em; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.35rem; }
    .v2-step-wrong { font-family: var(--ft); font-size: 1.0625rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 0.35rem; }
    .v2-step-tag { font-family: var(--fb); font-size: 0.6875rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #94a3b8; margin-right: 0.35rem; }
    .v2-step-right { font-family: var(--ft); font-size: 1.125rem; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .v2-step-body { font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; max-width: 52rem; }

    .v2-manifesto-block {
      font-family: var(--ft); font-weight: 700;
      font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.8vw, 1.85rem);
      line-height: 1.45;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 40rem;
      margin-inline: auto;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .v2-svc-card {
      background: var(--bg2);
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      text-align: left;
      transition: box-shadow 0.25s ease, border-color 0.25s ease;
    }
    .v2-svc-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.22);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.08);
    }
    .v2-svc-num { font-family: var(--fb); font-size: 0.625rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.15em; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }

    .v2-t-card {
      background: var(--bg2);
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .v2-t-desc { font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .v2-t-metric { font-family: var(--ft); font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.35rem); font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent); line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 0.35rem; }
    .v2-t-stat { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .v2-t-quote { font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--muted); font-style: italic; line-height: 1.55; }

    .v2-counters {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; text-align: center;
      margin-top: 2rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) { .v2-counters { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); } }
    .v2-cnum { font-family: var(--ft); font-size: clamp(1.85rem, 3.5vw, 2.75rem); font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent); display: block; }
    .v2-clabel { font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--muted); }

    .v2-faq-item { margin-bottom: 1.75rem; text-align: left; max-width: 40rem; margin-inline: auto; }
    .v2-faq-item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .v2-faq-q { font-family: var(--ft); font-size: 1.0625rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .v2-faq-a { font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; }

    .v2-sr-only {
      position: absolute; width: 1px; height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: -1px;
      overflow: hidden; clip: rect(0,0,0,0); white-space: nowrap; border: 0;
    }

    #s19 {
      background: var(--bg2); padding: 2rem var(--pad);
      display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
    }
    .s19-logo { font-family: var(--ft); font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; }
    .s19-contact, .s19-legal { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem; align-items: center; }
    .s19-sep { color: var(--muted); user-select: none; }
    .s19-contact a, .s19-legal a { font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; }
    .s19-contact a:hover, .s19-legal a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav id="v2-nav">
  <a href="/" class="v2-logo">{site.logoInitials}</a>
  <div class="v2-nav-right">
    <a href="/" class="v2-ver-link">← Version A</a>
    <a href="/contact" class="v2-cta">Book a Strategy Call</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<main class="v2-wrap">

  <section class="v2-center v2-hero-section" data-v2-hero-stage aria-busy="true">
    <div data-v2-hero-inner>
      <div
        class="v2-eyebrow v2-hero-eyebrow-wrap"
        data-v2-hero-eyebrow
        aria-label="For founders who've outgrown word of mouth"
      >
        <span class="v2-hero-eyebrow-line" data-v2-eyebrow-l1></span>
        <span class="v2-hero-eyebrow-line" data-v2-eyebrow-l2></span>
      </div>
      <div class="v2-hero-title-shell" data-v2-hero-title-shell>
        <h1
          class="v2-hero-title"
          data-v2-hero-title
          aria-label="We build personal brand positions that generate revenue."
        >
          <span class="v2-hero-title-prefix" data-v2-hero-title-prefix></span><span class="v2-hero-morph-clip" data-v2-hero-morph-clip><span data-v2-hero-morph class="v2-hero-morph-line"></span></span>
        </h1>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div data-v2-hero-rest>
      <p class="v2-p v2-p--wide">
        The kind where strangers contact you pre-sold, sales cycles halve, and your pipeline stops depending on who you had dinner with last quarter.
      </p>
      <p class="v2-p v2-p--wide v2-strong" style="margin-bottom:0">
        Book a strategy call to see how this applies to you.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="v2-btn">Book a Strategy Call</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="v2-center" style="margin-bottom:2rem">
      <span class="v2-eyebrow">The Invisible Authority Trap</span>
      <h2 class="v2-h2" data-v2-reveal-title>
        You've built a business that proves you're exceptional. Your market hasn't noticed yet.
      </h2>
      <p class="v2-p v2-p--wide">
        Your track record should be doing the selling. Instead, you're still the one doing the explaining.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="v2-pain-grid">
      <article class="v2-pain-card">
        <h3>The Referral Ceiling</h3>
        <p class="v2-pain-label">Your current reality:</p>
        <p class="v2-pain-quote">"Every client I have came through a warm introduction."</p>
        <p class="v2-pain-body">That's not a strategy. That's a dependency. Your revenue has a ceiling and it's the size of your personal network.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="v2-pain-card">
        <h3>The Content Treadmill</h3>
        <p class="v2-pain-label">Your current reality:</p>
        <p class="v2-pain-quote">"I'm posting, but the leads are lukewarm and the brand sounds like everyone else's."</p>
        <p class="v2-pain-body">Activity without architecture. You're feeding the algorithm. The algorithm is not feeding you back.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="v2-pain-card">
        <h3>The Competence Discount</h3>
        <p class="v2-pain-label">Your current reality:</p>
        <p class="v2-pain-quote">"I keep losing deals to people with half my experience but twice my visibility."</p>
        <p class="v2-pain-body">The market doesn't reward the best. It rewards the most legible. Right now, you're illegible.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="v2-pain-card">
        <h3>The Expertise Paradox</h3>
        <p class="v2-pain-label">Your current reality:</p>
        <p class="v2-pain-quote">"People who work with me are blown away. People who haven't, don't know I exist."</p>
        <p class="v2-pain-body">Your reputation is locked behind a door that only opens from the inside. Everyone who's in the room knows. No one outside it does.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
    <p class="v2-pull" data-v2-reveal-title>
      You don't have a marketing problem. You have a positioning problem. And it's costing you more than you think.
    </p>
    <p class="v2-center" style="margin-top:2rem">
      <a href="/contact" class="v2-btn">Book a Strategy Call</a>
    </p>
  </section>

  <section style="background:var(--bg2)">
    <div class="v2-center" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem">
      <span class="v2-eyebrow">The Position-First Method</span>
      <h2 class="v2-h2" data-v2-reveal-title>
        The market doesn't buy expertise. It buys the perception of expertise. We engineer that perception.
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="v2-p--wide" style="max-width:40rem;margin-inline:auto">
      <p class="v2-p v2-p--left" style="margin-bottom:1rem">Here's what nobody in this industry will say plainly:</p>
      <p class="v2-p v2-p--left">
        Your competitors aren't winning because they're better than you. They're winning because their market position does the selling before the conversation starts. By the time a prospect meets them, 70% of the decision is already made. Not by the pitch. Not by the proposal. By every signal the market absorbed before the first handshake.
      </p>
      <p class="v2-p v2-p--left">
        Your LinkedIn. Your media presence. Your speaking record. The way Google answers the question "Who is [your name]?" That's where deals are won or lost. And right now, your answer to that question is either silence, noise, or someone else's narrative.
      </p>
      <p class="v2-p v2-p--left">
        We reverse-engineer the exact perception that drives revenue in your specific market, then build every asset to make that perception the default. Not louder. Not more frequent. More precise.
      </p>
      <p class="v2-p v2-p--left" style="margin-bottom:0">
        This isn't content marketing with a strategy label. It's commercial positioning with content as one of several tools.
      </p>
    </div>
    <h2 class="v2-h2 v2-center" data-v2-reveal-title style="margin-top:2rem;margin-bottom:0">
      We don't make you louder. We make you inevitable.
    </h2>
    <p class="v2-center" style="margin-top:2rem">
      <a href="/contact" class="v2-btn">Book a Strategy Call</a>
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="v2-sr-only">Objections</h2>
    <div style="max-width:40rem;margin-inline:auto">
      <div class="v2-obj">
        <p class="v2-obj-q">"I've heard this before. Another agency promising 'strategic positioning.' Last one gave me a content calendar and a LinkedIn audit."</p>
        <div class="v2-obj-a">
          <p class="v2-p v2-p--left">We know. And we know why. Most agencies sell activity because activity is easy to deliver and easy to report on. "We posted 12 times this week" is a metric that sounds productive. It's also completely disconnected from revenue.</p>
          <p class="v2-p v2-p--left">Here's the question they never asked you: What specific perception does your market need to hold about you for revenue to follow? Not "what should we post." Not "which platforms." What must the market believe about you, specifically, that would make your ideal clients reach out without a referral?</p>
          <p class="v2-p v2-p--left" style="margin-bottom:0">That's where we start. Everything else is built to serve that answer.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="v2-obj">
        <p class="v2-obj-q">"Personal branding feels like self-promotion. I'm good at what I do. The work should speak for itself."</p>
        <div class="v2-obj-a">
          <p class="v2-p v2-p--left">It should. And in a perfect market, it would. But you don't operate in a perfect market. You operate in one where a founder with half your depth and a better LinkedIn presence is closing the deals you should be closing.</p>
          <p class="v2-p v2-p--left">We're not asking you to become a content creator. We're not asking you to perform. We're asking you to stop subsidising your competitors' advantage by staying invisible.</p>
          <p class="v2-p v2-p--left" style="margin-bottom:0">The work doesn't speak for itself. Positioning does. And then the work closes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="v2-obj">
        <p class="v2-obj-q">"I'm not sure personal branding delivers measurable ROI."</p>
        <div class="v2-obj-a">
          <p class="v2-p v2-p--left">Then you've been looking at the wrong agencies. Followers aren't ROI. Impressions aren't ROI. Media mentions aren't ROI.</p>
          <p class="v2-p v2-p--left">Inbound leads from people who have never been referred to you — that's ROI. A shorter sales cycle because the prospect already trusts you before the meeting — that's ROI. Winning a deal you didn't pitch for because your name was already in the room — that's ROI.</p>
          <p class="v2-p v2-p--left" style="margin-bottom:0">We measure what matters. If we can't tie it to revenue, we don't do it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="v2-center" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem">
      <span class="v2-eyebrow">Who we work with</span>
      <h2 class="v2-h2" data-v2-reveal-title>This isn't for everyone. That's the point.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="v2-split">
      <div class="v2-split-col v2-split-col--for">
        <h3>Who this is for</h3>
        <div class="v2-prose">
          <p>Entrepreneurs and founders, typically 40+, who've already built something that works.</p>
          <p>Annual revenue of €1M+. Established in your field. Known within your network, invisible outside it.</p>
          <p>Operating in sectors where trust isn't a differentiator — it's the transaction.</p>
          <p>You've probably tried some version of this before. An agency. A coach. A "brand strategist" who gave you a personal brand deck that's been gathering dust since 2022.</p>
          <p>You're not here because you believe in personal branding. You're here because you're tired of watching less qualified founders command the market position that should be yours.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="v2-split-col v2-split-col--not">
        <h3>Who we don't work with</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Founders looking for a social media manager with a strategy title.</li>
          <li>Anyone who measures success in followers, likes, or impressions.</li>
          <li>Entrepreneurs who want to "go viral." (Virality is a lottery ticket. Positioning is a pension.)</li>
          <li>Anyone not willing to invest at the level the outcome requires.</li>
          <li>Businesses without a proven offer. We position what works. We don't fix what doesn't.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
