      <h3 class="v2-h3">Strategic Visibility</h3>
      <p class="v2-p v2-p--left" style="margin:0;color:var(--muted);max-width:none">
        The right content, aimed at the right rooms, on the right platforms. Media, speaking, publishing, LinkedIn done with intent. Every asset earns its place. Nothing ships that doesn't serve the position.
      </p>
    </div>
